Better on the beach
The only Tiki Bar on Fort Lauderdale Beach, Bamboo Beach Club offers made-to-order dishes with Americana and Italian flair. Enjoy burgers, seafood, steaks, and the best pizza by the sand. Steps from the ocean, our Tiki Bar serves your favorite drinks while you catch live sports on flat screens and projection TVs. Open daily from 7 AM to 2 AM, with Happy Hour from 4-7 PM. Join us for events, great food, and unbeatable beach vibes.
Our Amazing Story
Welcome to our exceptional destination where your comfort and pleasure are our highest priorities. Relax and immerse yourself in our luxurious facilities, explore the beauty around you, and enjoy a truly memorable stay. Our dedicated team is ready to provide you with an unforgettable experience.
